{
  "stem": "14708.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 13.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were-- When would that be, approximately?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "This was all in, in the summer of 1944-- the summer of 1944.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There in the morning, we had to make the paper bags.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And in the afternoon, I had to go to different stores to sell it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And there was one epi-- I was not very good at that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I went into a store.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I asked the, the proprietor--",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The manager, yes, whether he wants to buy some paper bags.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, look, miss, a Jew would be doing this way.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He would look it up my name outside.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he would come in.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Hello, Mr.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Brown.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How are you doing today?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "We have excellent paper bags for you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that's the way you have to do it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was again such a memorable day, August 24, 1944.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This was Jan's 24th birthday.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we went to a restaurant for lunch.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 8,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Yeah, it was more like a milk bar or something like that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we were sitting with our lunch.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And suddenly at the door, three men came in, in two piece suit and hats-- fedoras.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we immediately knew that these are detectives.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And Jan told me, try to get out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because they were standing at the door.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Said to try to get out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I told him, I'm not going without you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Either I stay with you, or we are going together.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He said, don't be crazy.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "We have exactly the same papers.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In the moment they put it next to each other, we are both finished.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I have to pay, because this would be very strange, suspicious, running out without paying.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Go.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And then we said at what street and where should I wait.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "He will come after me.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
